title: PostgreSQL Expert
description: Demonstrated advanced knowledge of PostgreSQL database administration, optimization, and performance tuning. Successfully implemented complex queries, indexing strategies, and backup/recovery procedures.

title: Team Leadership
description: Led a cross-functional team of 5-8 engineers to successfully deliver a major project on time and within budget. Demonstrated effective communication, conflict resolution, and project management skills.

title: Effective Communication
description: Consistently delivers clear and concise presentations to both technical and non-technical audiences. Actively listens, asks clarifying questions, and adapts communication style to audience needs.
